{"tid":21951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺近一兩年皇馬巴塞開始調轉緊？","createTime":"2016-12-04T07:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T15:27:26.000Z","uid":9864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbb21b5163a51a900821326a9f0af6f76058d94","tid":21951,"uid":9864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"當初巴狗鐘意玩青訓，唔會亂買人，最多一季一個重磅收購加買後備兵，皇馬就瘋狂買唔信青訓。<br />\n<br />\n但自msn建立開始，巴狗買人買到癲撚左，皇馬就拖丹開始玩青訓，而買人就收斂左，當然，唔知關唔關比人禁轉會事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日巴狗盛世，睇黎今年皇馬盛世開始了，最少都玩番5.6.7年⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"ba9522be6c629db7b661029fcb2f2976c0fdcf12","tid":21951,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"吾皇有咩勁青訓踢緊"},{"pid":"2231ff361f9fc5008e5cc4627372d268d35bd457","tid":21951,"uid":9864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾皇有咩勁青訓踢緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華斯基斯 呀辛斯奧 莫拉達 卡華查 仲有琴晚果個唔知乜名，周中國皇盃入三球<br />\n<br />\n睇番巴狗最新既青訓，已經係10年出道既羅拔圖"},{"pid":"07f7976de2268fae0eb90cd11bf833a3c8337b5c","tid":21951,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"證明玩青訓先最勁, 安sir 要諗清楚"},{"pid":"9d0299f646c54ecdbbabd1094284dad49c12e2fb","tid":21951,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦負碌贏一場就係度吠<br />\n上季西甲邊個拎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38587c2ac6d0d4dff8179969b9b20edd52e26bfb","tid":21951,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收嗲啦負碌和一場就係度吠<br />\n上季西甲邊個拎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a1f4e3a09f41f3d0b04fb61eff17f9508ee05c43","tid":21951,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"根本兩間大球會不嬲都有青訓架啦，只差投放幾多資源同D後生仔打唔打到上黎，水平唔得咪要買人囉"},{"pid":"3dc6020a73155fcee176537e7357103cfb24c4f9","tid":21951,"uid"